title: Mickey Factz - #StoreRunner (TRU FOE DISS)
description:
Directed by Mr Good Evening

Mickey Factz ends the trilogy with a scathing diss entitled #STORERUNNER 
The story goes Aye Noun paid Tru Foe to diss Mickey Factz and Mickey proceeded to write 3 songs in under 20 hours from 2 am to 7 pm. Mind you he slept from 7 am to 11 am. So its really 16 hours. Anyway, Factz being the mc he is channeled his anger into one of the most catchiest and creative diss records to date. Long Live Lyricism.
